# dd LTP compliance lane — curated CORE syscall subset.
# Format:  <category>  <syscall>  <relpath-under-testcases/kernel/syscalls>
# Lines beginning with '#' are comments. One test per line.
# Curated to the surface dd emulates; multi-binary/helper-dependent, device-,
# hugepage-, cgroup-, module-, and privilege-heavy tests are intentionally
# excluded (see docs/compliance-ltp.md "Skipped / out-of-scope").

